

xe help --all|more. Show a list of XenServer CLI commands.
/etc/init.d/xapi 
Check the status of XAPI SERVERICE

xsconsole. Runs up the XenServer text based console.
xe host-dmesg
xe-toolstack-restart. Restarts the XenServer management tools.
ls –l. List files in a Directory.

netstat –s
Networking statistics

iostat -d 2 6
Storage traffic stats


VM-list
xe vm-list

VDI-list
XE vdi-list

SR list
XE sr-list


Logs###
tail –f /var/log/xensource.log
tail –f /var/log/xensource.log | grep "stop"

BAckup#
xe-backup-metadata -d –u [uuid of SR]


tcpdump –i [inf] –vvv –w [filename]

# top
xentop
List top Xen processes


mpstat 5
Processor stats in Dom0

vmstat 2
Virtual memory in Dom0

list_domains
Lists VMs that are running

pvs
Show local and remote LVHD SRs
